<p>If you've spent any time here, you've probably noticed I have a lot of hobbies. And if you know me in real life, you know that "a lot" is doing some heavy lifting in that sentence. Reading, gaming, building keyboards, tinkering with a 3D printer — there's always something going on.</p>

<p>One thing I love almost as much as the hobbies themselves is <em>tracking</em> them. This page is home base for all of that — a central hub for every catalog I maintain on this site. Pick one and dig in!</p>

